# .jenga_paths.example
#
# Copy this file to .jenga_paths and populate it with absolute paths to directories
# that should be searched for projects using the Jenga workflow.
#
# Rules:
#   - One absolute path per line
#   - Lines starting with # are comments
#   - Blank lines are ignored
#   - Each listed path is searched one level down (direct children) AND
#     two levels down (grandchildren) for directories containing jenga.config.json
#
# Example:
#
# /Users/yourname/Desktop/Projects
# /Users/yourname/work/clients
# /Users/yourname/repos
